    v1 = 0.0

    v1 = (((v0 + 0.82 + v2 + 0.96) * (v1 + 0.80 + tmp + 0.94)) / (wp.sin(v0 + 0.85) * (v2 + 0.93 * v1 + 0.82)))
    v1 = (v0 - (wp.abs(tmp + 0.13) - (v2 + 0.26 + tmp + 0.37)))
